## Success Metrics

- **Duplication**: < 30% text similarity between sequential responses
- **Consistency**: > 90% of responses match expected format
- **Relevance**: > 95% of responses stay on topic
- **Accuracy**: 0% hallucinated data when real data is available
- **User Satisfaction**: Positive feedback on response quality